@startuml
title Configure LLM (BYOK) - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "genai-service\nAdminLlmController" as Controller
participant "LlmConfigService" as Service
participant "AesGcmEncryptor" as Crypto
database "genai.llm_config" as DB
participant "LLM Provider" as LLM
participant "LlmClientHolder" as Holder

Admin -> Web: Enter base URL, model, API key
Web -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/admin/llm/validate
Gateway -> Controller: route with ADMIN JWT
Controller -> Service: validate(request)
Service -> LLM: test lightweight request
LLM --> Service: accepted / rejected
Controller --> Web: validation result

Admin -> Web: Save configuration
Web -> Gateway: PUT /api/v1/admin/llm/config
Gateway -> Controller: route
Controller -> Service: save(request)
Service -> Crypto: encrypt API key
Crypto --> Service: encryptedKey
Service -> DB: persist active config
Service -> Holder: rebuild active ChatClient
Controller --> Web: saved config with masked key
@enduml
